Vd2 (d2 0) vsource type=pwl wave=[0 0 0.80n 0 0.85n 1.8 1.60n 1.8 1.65n 0 2.40n 0 2.45n 0 3.20n 0 3.25n 1.8 4.20n 1.8]
Vd3 (d3 0) vsource type=pwl wave=[0 0 0.80n 0 0.85n 1.8 1.60n 1.8 1.65n 1.8 2.40n 1.8 2.45n 1.8 3.20n 1.8 3.25n 0 4.20n 0]
Vd4 (d4 0) vsource type=pwl wave=[0 0 0.80n 0 0.85n 1.8 1.60n 1.8 1.65n 1.8 2.40n 1.8 2.45n 1.8 3.20n 1.8 3.25n 0 4.20n 0]
Vd5 (d5 0) vsource type=pwl wave=[0 0 0.80n 0 0.85n 1.8 1.60n 1.8 1.65n 0 2.40n 0 2.45n 0 3.20n 0 3.25n 1.8 4.20n 1.8]
Vd6 (d6 0) vsource type=pwl wave=[0 0 0.80n 0 0.85n 1.8 1.60n 1.8 1.65n 0 2.40n 0 2.45n 1.8 3.20n 1.8 3.25n 0 4.20n 0]
